    <p>
        1. Fever<br>
   - Symptoms: Elevated body temperature, chills, sweating. <br>
   - Basic Cure: Over-the-counter fever reducers like acetaminophen (Tylenol) or ibuprofen (Advil, Motrin), plenty of fluids, and rest. <br>

2. Common Cold: <br>
   - Symptoms: Runny or stuffy nose, sore throat, cough, sneezing, mild body aches. <br>
   - Basic Cure: Rest, staying hydrated, over-the-counter cold medications (decongestants, antihistamines, pain relievers). <br>

3. Influenza (Flu): <br>
   - Symptoms: High fever, body aches, fatigue, cough, sore throat, runny or stuffy nose. <br>
   - Basic Cure: Antiviral medications (if prescribed by a doctor), rest, fluids, over-the-counter painkillers and fever reducers. <br>

4. Allergies: <br>
   - Symptoms: Sneezing, runny or stuffy nose, itchy/watery eyes, coughing, wheezing, skin rashes. <br>
   - Basic Cure: Avoiding allergens, over-the-counter antihistamines, nasal corticosteroids, decongestants, allergy shots (for severe cases). <br>

5. Headache: <br>
   - Symptoms: Pain or discomfort in the head or neck region. <br>
   - Basic Cure: Pain relievers such as acetaminophen, ibuprofen, aspirin, rest, hydration, stress management. <br>

6. Gastrointestinal Issues (e.g., Indigestion, Acid Reflux): <br>
   - Symptoms: Heartburn, stomach pain, bloating, nausea, vomiting, diarrhea, constipation. <br>
   - Basic Cure: Over-the-counter antacids, proton pump inhibitors (PPIs), H2 blockers, dietary changes, avoiding trigger foods, eating smaller meals. <br>

7. Urinary Tract Infections (UTIs): <br>
   - Symptoms: Frequent urge to urinate, pain or burning during urination, cloudy or strong-smelling urine, lower abdominal pain. <br>
   - Basic Cure: Antibiotics prescribed by a doctor, increased fluid intake, pain relievers (for discomfort). <br>


8. Muscle Strain/Sprain: <br>
   - Symptoms: Pain, swelling, limited range of motion, muscle weakness. <br>
   - Basic Cure: Rest, ice packs, compression, elevation (RICE method), over-the-counter pain relievers, physical therapy. <br>


